      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Dieter Bürßner</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:181px;\"><a href=\"http://www.rebel.nl/authors.htm\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/6/6b/Dieterbuerssner.jpg\" width=\"179\" height=\"227\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Dieterbuerssner.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Dieter Bürßner <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Dieter Bürßner</b>, (Dieter Buerssner, Dieter Bürssner)<br />\na German IT-architect, chess programmer, chemist and former member of the <i>The Steiner Research Group in </i>\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chemical_kinetics\">Photochemical Kinetics</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spin_chemistry\">Spin Chemistry</a><i> </i>\n<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> of the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Konstanz\">University of Konstanz</a>. \nDieter Bürßner started chess programming in the 80s, using <a href=\"/Atari_ST\" title=\"Atari ST\">Atari ST</a>, <a href=\"/IBM_PC\" title=\"IBM PC\">PC</a> and computers at the University, such as <a href=\"/VAX\" title=\"VAX\">VAX</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=MIPS&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"MIPS (page does not exist)\">MIPS</a> and others <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \nAfter some chess programming gaps, he started the development of his chess engine <a href=\"/Yace\" title=\"Yace\">Yace</a> in the early 90s.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dieter_B%C3%BCr%C3%9Fner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://chess.fsv.de/Pics/Paderborn2003/baderborn2003a.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"DieterUlf2003.JPG\" src=\"/images/0/0c/DieterUlf2003.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/IPCCC_2003\" title=\"IPCCC 2003\">IPCCC 2003</a> award ceremony, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a> (2nd with <a href=\"/Yace\" title=\"Yace\">Yace</a>) and <a href=\"/Ulf_Lorenz\" title=\"Ulf Lorenz\">Ulf Lorenz</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dieter_B%C3%BCr%C3%9Fner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.uni-konstanz.de/chemie/~ag_steiner/gruppe/steiner_ger.htm\">Ulrich Steiner</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>  (<b>1990</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/30017584_Theoretical_Treatment_of_Magnetic_Field_Dependent_In-cage_Backward_Electron_Transfer_During_Photooxidation_of_RuII_Complexes\">Theoretical Treatment of Magnetic Field Dependent In-cage Backward Electron Transfer During Photooxidation of Ru(II) Complexes</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zeitschrift_f%C3%BCr_Physikalische_Chemie\">Zeitschrift für Physikalische Chemie</a>, Vol. 169, Part 2</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.uni-konstanz.de/chemie/~ag_steiner/1+group.htm\">Hans-Joachim Wolff</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.uni-konstanz.de/chemie/~ag_steiner/gruppe/steiner_ger.htm\">Ulrich Steiner</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/30017576_Magnetokinetic_Probing_of_Extremely_Fast_Electron_Spin_Relaxation_in_Paramagnetic_Ruthenium_Complexes\">Magnetokinetic Probing of Extremely Fast Electron Spin Relaxation in Paramagnetic Ruthenium Complexes</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zeitschrift_f%C3%BCr_Physikalische_Chemie\">Zeitschrift für Physikalische Chemie</a>, Vol. 182</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.uni-konstanz.de/chemie/~ag_steiner/1+group.htm\">Hans-Joachim Wolff</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.uni-konstanz.de/chemie/~ag_steiner/gruppe/steiner_ger.htm\">Ulrich Steiner</a> (<b>1994</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/30017375_Magnetic_Spin_Effects_on_Photooxidation_Quantum_Yields_of_RuII-trisbipyridine_Type_Complexes_in_Magnetic_Fields_up_to_175_Tesla\">Magnetic Spin Effects on Photooxidation Quantum Yields of RuII-tris(bipyridine) Type Complexes in Magnetic Fields up to 17.5 Tesla</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Angewandte_Chemie\">Angewandte Chemie</a>, Vol. 33, No. 17</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.uni-konstanz.de/chemie/~ag_steiner/gruppe/steiner_ger.htm\">Ulrich Steiner</a> (<b>1994</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/30017577_Spin_Chemistry_of_RuII-Trisdiimine_Complex_Photooxidation_in_Magnetic_Fields_up_to_175_Tesla\">Spin Chemistry of Ru(II)-Trisdiimine Complex Photooxidation in Magnetic Fields up to 17.5 Tesla</a></i>.  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coordination_Chemistry_Reviews\">Coordination Chemistry Reviews</a>, Vol. 132</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dieter_B%C3%BCr%C3%9Fner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dieter_B%C3%BCr%C3%9Fner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=114010\">Problems with winboard protocol (Crafty 17.10 vs Yace)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 10, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=133755\">King, rook pawn and wrong bishop endgames</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 18, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Wrong_Color_Bishop_and_Rook_Pawn\" title=\"Wrong Color Bishop and Rook Pawn\">Wrong Color Bishop and Rook Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=156036\">Yace in Paderborn</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 26, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=163888\">Parallel algorithms in chess programming</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 16, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/ABDADA\" title=\"ABDADA\">ABDADA</a>, <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=194764\">Nice Stalemate Trap by Tinker</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 29, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Stalemate\" title=\"Stalemate\">Stalemate</a>, <a href=\"/Tinker\" title=\"Tinker\">Tinker</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=224950\">Question to Dieter Buerssner</a> by <a href=\"/Alvaro_Cardoso\" title=\"Alvaro Cardoso\">Alvaro Cardoso</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 21, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=278666\">Yace at CCT5</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 21, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/CCT5\" title=\"CCT5\">CCT5</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=306858\">Another memory latency test</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 17, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Memory\" title=\"Memory\">Memory</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=339225\">Re: De Bruijn Sequence Generator</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 30, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/BitScan\" title=\"BitScan\">BitScan</a>, <a href=\"/De_Bruijn_Sequence_Generator\" title=\"De Bruijn Sequence Generator\">De Bruijn Sequence Generator</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=352781\">Wrong Colored B and Rook Pawn Positions for Engines (and Humans?)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 04, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Wrong_Color_Bishop_and_Rook_Pawn\" title=\"Wrong Color Bishop and Rook Pawn\">Wrong Color Bishop and Rook Pawn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=364329\">Bug/glitch in Nalimov Code (and in Wilhelm)?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 09, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Wilhelm\" title=\"Wilhelm\">Wilhelm</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=379228\">Re: full documentation of yace commands</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 27, 2004</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dieter_B%C3%BCr%C3%9Fner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=407134\">Subject: Problem (small bug?) with Nalimov TBs</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 23, 2005&#160;» <a href=\"/Nalimov_Tablebases\" title=\"Nalimov Tablebases\">Nalimov Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=427356\">(long) Some Statistics from Pavel's Yace Paderborn vs. Aristrach 4.5</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 21, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=447238\">Re: Is chess knowledge always meaningful? (An Example)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 03, 2005</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dieter_B%C3%BCr%C3%9Fner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/dieter-b%C3%BCr%C3%9Fner-5353b45b/\">Dieter Bürßner | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.horst-wandersleben.de/Wette.htm\">Computerschach - Eine Wette, die ich gerne verloren habe</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Horst_Wandersleben&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Horst Wandersleben (page does not exist)\">Horst Wandersleben</a> (German)&#160;» <a href=\"/Fifty-move_Rule\" title=\"Fifty-move Rule\">Fifty-move Rule</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Dieter_B%C3%BCr%C3%9Fner&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.rebel.nl/authors.htm\">Meet the Authors</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.uni-konstanz.de/chemie/~ag_steiner/\">The Steiner Research Group</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chemical_kinetics\">Photochemical Kinetics</a> \nand <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spin_chemistry\">Spin Chemistry</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Konstanz\">Universität Konstanz</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Lars_Bremer\" title=\"Lars Bremer\">Lars Bremer</a> (<b>2004</b>). <i>Das Rückwärts-Genie</i>. <a href=\"/Computerschach_und_Spiele\" title=\"Computerschach und Spiele\">CSS 4/04</a> (German), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lbremer.de/artikel/Yace.pdf\">pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20041103061005fw_/http://www.fsv.de/chess-server/Pics/Paderborn2003/baderborn2003a.htm\">FSV personal chess service - Paderborn 2003 Pics</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Torsten_Schoop&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Torsten Schoop (page does not exist)\">Torsten Schoop</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>), Victory Ceremony: Dieter Bürssner, 2nd place</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dieter Bürßner</a> found a game finished in a <a href=\"/Fifty-move_Rule\" title=\"Fifty-move Rule\">fifty-move rule</a> draw, where <a href=\"/Castling\" title=\"Castling\">castling</a> occurred during the last fifty moves</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228175900\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.020 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.023 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 101/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 210/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighe